### Statistics Service

### 1. 월별 구매 상세 내역 조회
# chosenMonth format: YYYY-MM (Assumed based on naming)
GET http://localhost:8000/api/v1/ingredient-stock-service/statistics/monthly?chosenMonth=2026-01
Authorization: Bearer {{auth_token}}

### 2. 재료별 구매 통계 조회
# Note: URL contains typo 'ingreient' as defined in controller
GET http://localhost:8000/api/v1/ingredient-stock-service/statistics/ingreient
Authorization: Bearer {{auth_token}}

### 3. 카테고리별 지출 통계 조회
GET http://localhost:8000/api/v1/ingredient-stock-service/statistics/category
Authorization: Bearer {{auth_token}}

### 4. 폐기 비용 조회
# startDate, endDate format: YYYY-MM-DD
GET http://localhost:8000/api/v1/ingredient-stock-service/statistics/disposal?startDate=2026-01-01&endDate=2026-01-31
Authorization: Bearer {{auth_token}}

### 5. 월별 폐기 내역 조회
GET http://localhost:8000/api/v1/ingredient-stock-service/statistics/monthly-disposal
Authorization: Bearer {{auth_token}}
